title: Vengeance Dirty Electro Vol.3
description:
Vengeance Dirty Electro Vol.3, an ultra-heavy arsenal for creating head-banging club music is back with a brand new samplepack!


More devastating than ever with 40 club-smashing construction kits waiting to be discovered. For your convenience, all the oneshots have been organized into their own separate folder. Styles covered by this expansion include Complextro, Dubstep, Dirty Dutch, Bigroom, Festival, and Electrohouse. Don't waste your time with other weak libraries - get the original. This is the real Dirty Electro!

Dowmloaded from Rutracker
